{"word":"Rebekah","slug":"rebekah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rebekah</b> <a href=\"#/H7259\">H7259</a> <br/> Daughter of Bethuel, grandniece of Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=23'>Gen 22:23</a><br/> Becomes Isaac's wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=67'>Gen 24:67</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=20'>Gen 25:20</a><br/> Mother of Esau and Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=28'>Gen 25:28</a><br/> Passes as Isaac's sister<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=11'>Gen 26:11</a><br/> Displeased with Esau's wives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=35'>Gen 26:35</a><br/> Prompts Jacob to deceive Isaac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=29'>Gen 27:29</a><br/> Sends Jacob to Laban<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=46'>Gen 27:46</a><br/> Burial place of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=31'>Gen 49:31</a><br/> Called Rebecca<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=10'>Rom 9:10</a>"}]}